<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ExecIntel | Demo</title>

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0b1220;
      --panel:#0f172a;
      --text:#ffffff;
      --muted:#cbd5e1;
      --border: rgba(148,163,184,.18);
      --accent:#38bdf8;
      --accentHover:#0ea5e9;
      --radius: 18px;
      --shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    }
    *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 50% -10%, rgba(56,189,248,.16), transparent 55%),
                  var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
    }
    a{ color: inherit; text-decoration:none; }
    .wrap{ width:min(1100px, 92%); margin:0 auto; }

    header{
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      background: rgba(11,18,32,.68);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      padding: 14px 0;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .4px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .brand .dot{
      width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(56,189,248,.55);
    }
    nav ul{
      list-style:none;
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap: 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.86);
    }
    nav a{
      padding: 10px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: background .2s ease;
    }
    nav a:hover{ background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color:#07121f;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, background .2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(56,189,248,.18);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn:hover{
      background: var(--accentHover);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(56,189,248,.22);
    }
    .btn.secondary{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color: var(--text);
      box-shadow: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .btn.secondary:hover{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    main{ padding: 38px 0 70px 0; }
    h1{
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
      text-align:center;
    }
    p{
      margin: 0 auto 22px auto;
      max-width: 820px;
      text-align:center;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .video-card{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    video{
      width: 100%;
      display:block;
      background:#000;
    }
    .meta{
      padding: 14px 16px 16px 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    footer{
      padding: 26px 0;
      color: rgba(148,163,184,.9);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align:center;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="wrap nav">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span>EXECINTEL</span>
      </div>

      <nav aria-label="Primary">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="index.html#how">How It Works</a></li>
          <li><a href="demo.html" aria-current="page">Demo</a></li>
          <li><a href="index.html#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center;">
        <a class="btn secondary" href="index.html">← Back</a>
        <a
          class="btn"
          href="https://aistudio.google.com/apps/36313336-7808-4aca-a5b5-9d0d380f56c2?source=&showPreview=true&showAssistant=true"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          Analyze Earnings →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>ExecIntel Demo</h1>
    <p>
      Watch a quick walkthrough of the ExecIntel “Intelligence Brief” experience.
      (Make sure <b>execintel-demo.mp4</b> is in the same folder as this file.)
    </p>

    <div class="video-card">
      <video controls playsinline preload="metadata" poster="execintel-hero.png">
        <source src="execintel-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
      <div class="meta">
        Tip: Export the Runway video in <b>16:9</b> for the cleanest look on the web.
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 ExecIntel — Strategic Intelligence Assistant
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
